### {500}{}{Don't you see it by now? Tweaking this, filling that... Mostly, I'm trying to provide our fellas with weapons they can shoot, not dig holes in the ground. Just imagine: you are young dashing Jackal, going to raid, trying to loot something far away from here - and there are some hungry mad creatures ambushing you - RRAWR! And they are biting your legs! And you would be glad to blast their ass off with your favorite sawed-off - but it's jammed! That's when - right before death - you remember that you, for a long time already, didn't take your gun to old man Carl for maintenance...}
{500}{}{你现在没看到吗？调整这个，填充那个。。。大多数情况下，我试图为我们的家伙提供他们可以射击的武器，而不是在地上挖洞。想象一下：你是一个年轻的潇洒的豺狼，要去突袭，试图抢劫离这里很远的东西――而有一些饥饿的疯狂生物在伏击你――RRAWR！他们在咬你的腿！你会很高兴用你最喜欢的锯掉的东西把他们的屁股炸飞――但它卡住了！就在那时――就在死前――你还记得，很长一段时间以来，你都没有把枪交给卡尔老人维修。。。 -- Don't you see it by now? Tweaking this, filling that... Mostly, I'm trying to provide our fellas with weapons they can shoot, not dig holes in the ground. Just imagine: you are young dashing Jackal, going to raid, trying to loot something far away from here - and there are some hungry mad creatures ambushing you - RRAWR! And they are biting your legs! And you would be glad to blast their ass off with your favorite sawed-off - but it's jammed! That's when - right before death - you remember that you, for a long time already, didn't take your gun to old man Carl for maintenance...}
