### {700}{}{As I said - you did broke something, ain't ya? Everything you touch, you break! How you can even be like that? Man, gimme that piece of yours... [he examines engine for some time] ...Yes, just as I suspected... You already toyed with it, right? Did you try to break it on purpose?}
{700}{}{正如我所说，你确实打碎了一些东西，不是吗？你碰的东西都会碎！你怎么会那样？伙计，把你的那块给我。。。[他检查了发动机一段时间]。。。是的，正如我所怀疑的。。。你已经玩过了，对吧？你是故意打破它的吗？ -- As I said - you did broke something, ain't ya? Everything you touch, you break! How you can even be like that? Man, gimme that piece of yours... [he examines engine for some time] ...Yes, just as I suspected... You already toyed with it, right? Did you try to break it on purpose?}
